Products.Name: Projector Plus
Products.Description:
The HD Projector gives the home theater enthusiast HD output at a super low price. It has a compact design and is both easy to install and setup. The combination of its size and power means that this widescreen HD Projector will give you hours of enjoyment without a big blow to your wallet.
New for this year’s model is super-focus technology - with the push of a single button, the HD Projector automatically focuses and adjusts colors so you do not have to manually ﬁ ne-tune picture quality. Once you press the button, the HD Projector begins a series of internal tests to determine the best possible picture based on ambient light within your home theater.
